sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Customer
    participant Onboarding as KYC Onboarding
    participant IDV as Identity Verification
    participant Screening as Sanctions/PEP Screening
    participant Risk as Risk Engine
    participant EDD as EDD Team
    participant Monitoring as Ongoing Monitoring
    participant Review as Periodic Review
    participant Exit as Exit Decision

    Customer->>Onboarding: Apply for account<br/>(name, DOB, address, ID)
    Onboarding->>IDV: Verify identity
    IDV->>IDV: Document check (OCR, NFC)<br/>Liveness + biometric match<br/>Database verification
    IDV-->>Onboarding: Verified / Failed

    Onboarding->>Screening: Screen name against lists
    Screening->>Screening: OFAC SDN, EU, UN,<br/>PEP databases,<br/>adverse media
    Screening-->>Onboarding: Clear / Hit

    alt Screening hit
        Onboarding->>EDD: Escalate for review
        EDD-->>Onboarding: Cleared / Blocked
    end

    Onboarding->>Risk: Assess customer risk
    Risk->>Risk: Score based on:<br/>geography, product, entity type,<br/>PEP status, industry, source of funds
    Risk-->>Onboarding: Low / Medium / High

    alt High risk
        Onboarding->>EDD: Enhanced Due Diligence
        EDD->>EDD: Source of wealth,<br/>source of funds,<br/>senior management approval
        EDD-->>Onboarding: Approved / Declined
    end

    Onboarding-->>Customer: Account opened

    Note over Monitoring: Continuous throughout relationship

    loop Ongoing monitoring
        Customer->>Monitoring: Transactions
        Monitoring->>Monitoring: Transaction monitoring<br/>Sanctions rescreening<br/>Adverse media alerts
    end

    loop Periodic review (1-3-5 years based on risk)
        Review->>Review: Refresh KYC data<br/>Rescreen<br/>Reassess risk rating
        Review-->>Customer: Request updated docs if needed
    end

    alt Risk becomes unacceptable
        Review->>Exit: Recommend exit
        Exit->>Exit: Senior approval<br/>File SAR if needed<br/>Close account
        Exit-->>Customer: Relationship terminated
    end
